Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 喵波羅的問卷調查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:38.58,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)\an8}請協助「銀河貓喵波羅」的問卷調查。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}加上這些基本都收齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.74,0:03:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家好像都玩得很開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做得好 空太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.33,0:03:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是因為大家都很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的職位換了別人來做結果應該也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}挺有風度的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對此我也算有冷靜分析過的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖然只有一點點 我感到更自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還在向『一起做遊戲吧』投稿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是的 在那之後馬上就投了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在正在等結果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赤坂提醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為了防止再犯同樣的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要細心地看喵波羅檢討會的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我以此為基礎 製作了一份企劃書
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然後呢 有多少自信？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}相當有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.25,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\be10\blur3\fad(450,350)\an9}投稿完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.41,0:04:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哦 不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.71,0:04:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 說起龍之介的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}麗塔小姐真大膽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自從那以來 她就不斷的對我郵件轟炸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後我受不了 還是把赤坂的信箱位址告訴她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那小女僕一定很生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 那可謂是怒氣衝天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那兩個人要是能有進展就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兩人一起來有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.36,0:04:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真白跑來找神田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想大概在這裡 就帶她過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找我有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是有事才來找我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個…我不懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}別問我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.26,0:05:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}發現大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼辦啊 學弟 千載難逢的機會到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不知道你在說什…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大白天的你就襲擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為人家等不及到晚上嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.87,0:05:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我感到自身有危險 今晚就在外留宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給你 仁 我為你做了便當
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.75,0:05:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 仁學長剛才不是剛吃了麵包來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HA65EFF&\blur8\pos(645.714,114.429)}愛❤你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HA65EFF&\blur8\pos(645.714,114.429)}愛❤你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&HA65EFF&\blur8\pos(645.714,114.429)}愛❤你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如何 我抓住你的胃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我還沒吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真白 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼想吃的菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}結果椎名那傢伙到底是來做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山你心情好像不太好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}下次我會做更豪華的便當給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名的心事 神田你不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.91,0:06:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}明天也敬請期待哦 仁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 你明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明白 但是不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}仁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.58,0:06:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得說這種話一點也不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我人才沒有那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.55,0:06:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感覺青山你偶爾像在欺負我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才不管呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 下個月聖誕節啊 感覺好沒勁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了？難道彌生你有預定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和壘球社的社員們一起開派對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是小孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}繭你有預定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}七海呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神田呢 你有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有何打算 就算你這麼問…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我說你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在又有傳言說神田在和椎名交往哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要再爭氣一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對對 不然很對不起宮原啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.09,0:07:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是我已經好好拒絕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼你們會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看到宮原那樣子誰都能明白的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之 不明確一點可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.90,0:07:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H32&\fs30\bord1\shad0\3c&H6D4B9D&\c&HBB90F6&\frz4.126\pos(680,364.428)\frx346\fry358\be1}致仁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…那個 三鷹學長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喲 青山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個 難道是情書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也算是類似的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.09,Note,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H9AA9D8&\pos(373,156)}結婚登記書
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恭 恭喜您結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一點都不好笑哦 青山同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是上井草學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 我有件東西想交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.86,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\be10\blur3\fad(450,350)}Happy White Christmas
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和別人一起去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是戲劇的票 我真的可以收下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原本是從麻美學姐那裡收到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不過她好像不方便一起去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我總不能拿去邀請別的女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以就給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 上演時間是在平安夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要好好利用小道具哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}椎名 如果我在換衣服的時候把內褲脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:08:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敲門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:08:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太遲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這次也沒什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}答應我你不生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你說這種話的時候通常都是要說些驚天動地的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是很普通的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就不要說這種奇怪的前提啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.22,0:09:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想做便當是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.18,0:09:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋 別摟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聽好了 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人類蘊藏著美妙的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.98,0:09:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但 即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也有著絕對做不到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}人無法長出翅膀 要接受這件事實！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}仁學長你為什麼就給她穿上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好看嗎 空太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}給我脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}噢噢 沒想到一張口就如此大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓椎名做料理絕對會出大問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.67,0:10:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在我看來你只是躍躍欲試罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我接下來要去見留美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.67,0:10:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下來就是兩位年輕人的時間囉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦？等等 仁學長…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}來做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.76,0:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}料理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼變成一個詞一個詞的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.14,0:10:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但你不是要畫原稿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且還有之前文化祭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}豈不是比預定計劃慢下來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原稿我晚點再畫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說什麼晚點再畫 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道了啦 教你就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}主菜是香炸鯖魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再配上煎蛋和沙拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就先從煎蛋開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先從煎蛋開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒有必要複述了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:11:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把蛋像這樣在大碗邊敲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敲出裂縫之後像這樣將其分成兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.94,0:11:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要試試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分成兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我現在有種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看到自己孩子第一次能做成點事情時父母的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太 菜刀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行 要等你水平提升之後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我已經可以打雞蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你才只會這個而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.92,0:11:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我喜歡菜刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你到底對菜刀傾注了多少感情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}愛到晚上都睡不著覺的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就讓你用菜刀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是襲擊人時的拿法吧…啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣拿起來比較順手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an8}別對著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你到底想料理什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想被我料理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.31,0:11:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做菜對椎名而言實在太困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}No more菜刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就給我正常地拿刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}記好了 沒有拿菜刀的那隻手是貓的手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貓的手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}沒錯 絕對不要切到自己的手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？ 黃瓜頂端…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胃有被抓住嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.51,0:12:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果我的胃就這樣被抓住的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是說我的胃被種黃瓜的農戶抓住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做菜真是高深莫測
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只不過是切了黃瓜頂端的你又明白什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我繼續切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}記得是貓的手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}貓的手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}笨蛋… 手給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老師 椎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 這樣就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}當然是拿你出氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼老實地道歉幹什麼 真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:13:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原稿沒問題嗎 截稿日期是明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還剩下扉頁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之記得先聯絡一下編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放棄做菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.74,0:13:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不做比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太不希望我做菜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不希望你再受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.45,0:13:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了 我去聯絡綾乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.65,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直到不久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直到不久之前 明明都還覺得她就好像僅僅為了畫漫畫而活著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}聖誕禮物我就要哥哥了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}請問您找哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.54,0:14:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對不起 十分抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有什麼事嗎 優子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哥哥 發生怪異現象了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明打的是哥哥的電話卻打到別人那裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這也算是一種怪異現象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.94,0:14:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 能佔用你一點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我喜歡茶色的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她的原稿來得及畫完嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看那個樣子今天就能交稿了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}手指上的傷看起來也無大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坦白地告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.00,0:14:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你覺得最近的椎名如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}例如變漂亮了 變可愛了 令你想要抱住她之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.17,0:15:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想要我說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這個先放一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就放一邊去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不覺得椎名她有點變了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}初次見面時 她完全是一副藝術家的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和她說話時會有一種不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以一副望穿一切的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}似乎在看著我 又似乎沒在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就好像是遠離了塵世一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我第一次見到她的時候也是那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在不一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我想做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原稿我晚些再畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.34,0:15:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 看著現在的椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}心頭就無法平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像是有種異樣的感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不舒服…也不完全是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}讓我覺得心煩意亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.27,0:15:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那還真是寶貴的見解呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}之前明明滿腦子都只有漫畫 對其他事都毫不關心的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在突然說什麼想要做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在的椎名 很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就好像不是真正的椎名了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.08,0:16:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我倒覺得現在這樣才比較正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是指作為一個女孩子很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 她還有一些迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一直以來除了學畫以外什麼都沒有接觸過的她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.93,0:16:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}現在體驗著像普通高中生一樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去理解何為「普通」是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 如果她因此會失去自己特有的世界觀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看來作為一個編輯我考慮的太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.62,0:16:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她所擁有的才能和經驗 事到如今已經無法動搖了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以前的椎名和現在的椎名 你喜歡哪一個？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你 你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是 無論選擇哪一邊都意味著你喜歡她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我覺得 比起現在的椎名 原本的她更讓我覺得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}空太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在這做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原稿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}畫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我問你在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就是因為這才受傷了的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果這次又受傷 短時間內恢復不了的話該怎麼辦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.94,0:18:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}集中精力在漫畫的連載上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原稿…已經畫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不久之前的你會畫的更多！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不是還說要把畫的質量提升至極致嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能夠畫畫的傢伙就別給我做什麼偷工減料的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.59,0:18:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要這麼說的話 你要這麼說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就從我的心裡走開！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這算什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不懂 這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以說…你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.19,0:18:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告訴我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告訴我 空太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.65,Note,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\c&H4D5E62&\frz348.7\pos(572,53)}年終聯歡會的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.54,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雖說還有點早 這是出版社年終聯歡會的通知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.46,0:19:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我忘記交給椎名了 能幫我轉交給她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}錯過給她的時機了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}學弟 我有事找你商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼是迷你裙聖誕老人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因為馬上就到聖誕節啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有一個多月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小細節就不要在意啦 快上樓到我的房間裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要坐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}說不定他平安夜已經有約了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再說我們明明沒有在交往 好難啟齒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}美咲學姐說有事商量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}對了 你也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.84,0:19:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底要怎麼做我才能把心意傳達給仁？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.85,0:19:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我實在看不出這是充滿煩惱的人會穿的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.73,0:20:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我明明都像這樣熱情滿滿地告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}為什麼仁就是察覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那個 學姐所謂的熱情告白指的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在便當裡面寫著「愛你」 你們都知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}還有把結婚登記書放到他的鞋櫃裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}婚…婚姻登記書？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再之後 把他叫到校舍後面告白時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他就說「好冷啊 我們回去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把他叫到體育館後面告白時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他又說「好睏啊 我們回去吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全被無視了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我竭盡努力 但全都被他當成是玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以 我決定採取最後的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.10,0:20:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後的手段？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.81,0:20:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平安夜 希望你們能讓我和仁獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}助我一臂之力吧 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}商量之前就已經有結論了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青山？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能去你的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在這裡說就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我有兩張戲劇的票 你願意和我一起去…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}戲劇？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 不過是在平安夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.18,0:21:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 那可是24號啊 就這樣跟我約好可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正大家也都沒空 沒什麼關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那約好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不准反悔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這麼不信任我的話 要不要勾手指？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.70,0:21:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}約好囉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.95,0:21:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 約好了
Comment: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.86,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,ED2
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:20.40,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ありふれた感情から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:20.40,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}那些紛紛擾擾的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:24.13,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}卒業もできてなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.40,0:22:24.15,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}至今無法從中畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:27.20,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}眠れない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.16,0:22:27.20,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}輾轉難眠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.79,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}突然の雨抜かるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.79,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}不經意間突然下起大雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:34.50,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}あの靴は瞬きする
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.79,0:22:34.50,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}那雙鞋子隨之開始閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:40.92,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君の世界をきっと受け止めている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.50,0:22:40.92,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一定正在接受你的整個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:44.26,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}君のリアル 僕の視線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:44.26,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}你的現實 我的視線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:47.55,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}どこが違うと知っても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:47.55,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就算明白有所不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:54.52,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}あのくだびれたTシャツみたいにさせないから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:54.52,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}也不會讓其變得跟那條破舊的T恤一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:56.14,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Prime number
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:56.14,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Prime number
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:23:01.86,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界にどれひとつとして同じものがない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.14,0:23:01.86,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}世界上不存在任何完全相同的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.41,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}心の空白を無理に塗れなくてもいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.86,0:23:08.41,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}所以無需強行塗滿心中的空白哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:15.87,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}たくさんの誰かの記憶に残されているよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.41,0:23:15.87,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}比起在許多人的心中留下回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:23.02,ED-R2-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}屋根の上君だけの空になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:23.02,ED-R2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我更喜歡成為只屬於你的屋上青空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明明是平安夜 我在動搖什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:40.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs43\alpha&H00&\1a&H00&\3a&H00&\shad0\blur3\3c&H2497D9&\pos(700,450)\4c&H26BBAF&\c&HFFFFFF&\b1}平安夜的窗邊和點點燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}話說 這還是我有生以來第一次和女生一起過的聖誕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哇 難度突然變高了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}總之為了能冷靜下來 玩會兒DQ10吧
